# Line-ending policy is repo-owned (overrides each machine's core.autocrlf):
# all text files are stored AND checked out with LF, on every OS. Python, uv,
# ruff, pytest and modern Windows editors all handle LF working trees fine —
# this kills CRLF-vs-LF diff noise between the Windows laptop and the Linux
# GPU workstation in both directions.
* text=auto eol=lf
